// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P131773372" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Get Rich Quick</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You overhear a couple of Freakshow thugs talking about a job their boss is pulling off.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>You eavesdrop on a pair of Freakshow going on about their boss <color red>t3h l00t3r3r's</color> most recent exploits.  Evidently he's teamed up with that wackjob Shock Treatment to take out an incredibly wealthy and influential psychologist, Dr. Elena Walker.  You're not sure what their particular beef with this woman is, but you see an opportunity to make some quick cash.</scale></font></color><br><br>Just two years ago this Dr. Elena Walker won several million dollars for a Nobel Peace Prize.  If you swoop in there and play the 'hero' she'll likely be willing to part with some of that sweet cash."
// Answer Text :
"P3197228306" "HERO: Liberate Dr. Walker and some of her excess cash!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


