// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1440197018" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Tempting Proposal</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Your cell phone rings.  You've got an interesting text message.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>You receive the following message on your phone:</scale></color><color orange><br><br>'{HeroName},<br>I've been following your work for some time now and I understand you're working from within Paragon City.  I have a job offer for you that is incredibly lucratrive.  One of our ex-organization members recently left us, I want him dead.  He's joined up with Arachnos and has been working closely with Westin Phipps.  If you're not familiar with this scumbag, know that he's been responsible for heinous crimes in the Rogue Isles that keep the masses uneducated, starving and living in squallor.  Your target is Maxwell West, he's been untouchable by law enforcement and private organizations like Longbow.  This is why I come to you.  Eliminate Mr. West and I will pay you handsomely.<br><br>-J'</scale></font></color><br><br>.  This sounds too good to be true.  There's definitely a catch.  There's always a catch.  You've got a sneaking suspicion that this 'J' character is up to no good and is looking to play you and then not pay you.  It would be fun to throw a monkey wrench into 'J's' plan."
// Answer Text :
"P3303830492" "HERO: Find out what J is up to."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


