// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1952450820" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Arachnos Summons Order</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You are approached by an Arachnos messenger who hastily delivers a letter and runs for his life.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>You flip the black piece of plastic over noticing the red emblazed Arachnos spider logo on its cover.  Upon opening it you see the following message:</scale></font></color><br><br><color orange>Greetings {HeroName},<br><br>I have been tasked by Lord Recluse himself to bring you back to the Isles.  I have been given files outlining all of your 'heinous' deeds within the Rogue Isles and will expose them all to the public of Paragon City if you do not comply with this summons.  All you are required to do at this time is to go to the coordinates located below and kill the target being held by the Arachnos agents there.  Comply and you will receive a full pardon from Lord Recluse for your treachery. Fail to comply and you will be exposed for what you truly are.  That, and I'll personally tear you limb from limb.<br><br>-Mangle</color><br><br>Who does Lord Recluse think he is?  King of the world?  Okay, maybe he does, but that doesn't mean he can try and intimidate you.  That said, there might be a way to profit off of this situation and still look good in the eyes of the public."
// Answer Text :
"P1360189931" "HERO: Investigate Arachnos Summons"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


