// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P2979662567" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Loose Lips Sink Ships</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You overhear some gossiping Tsoo...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>You eavesdrop on some low ranking Tsoo thugs and find out that they've kidnapped the multi-billionaire Harold Vanderton's family, and local heroes have so far been incapable of locating their whereabouts. In desperation he has offered a substantial reward to anyone with information that leads to the return of his family.</color></font></scale><br><br>Through your circle of street contacts you have a pretty good idea where to find these cash cows. You save the people and earn the big bucks, the only thing that stands in your way are the Tsoo."
// Answer Text :
"P1279842136" "HERO: Make the Tsoo pay, and the billionaire too."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
